OL,3,CFuneral held for girl stabbed in street
OL,5,FFamily and friends have attended the
OL,6,Ffuneral of a 16-year-old girl who was
OL,7,Fstabbed to death in a street in Leeds.
OL,9,FChloe Watson Dransfield died following
OL,10,Fan incident in Kennerleigh Avenue,
OL,11,FAusthorpe, on 28 March.
OL,13,FA horse-drawn carriage carrying a pink
OL,14,Fcoffin and bearing Chloe's image led
OL,15,Fthe funeral cortege from her home in
OL,16,FGomersal to Dewsbury Crematorium on
OL,17,FTuesday.
OL,19,FNearly #23,000 was raised for Chloe's
OL,20,Ffuneral through an online appeal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
