OL,3,CFuneral held for girl stabbed in street
OL,5,FChloe's cousin Shantelle Watson, who
OL,6,Fset up the fundraising page, said: "We
OL,7,Fwould like to say a heartfelt thank
OL,8,Fyou to everyone who has kindly donated
OL,9,Fmoney to help us give Chloe the send-
OL,10,Foff she truly deserves.
OL,12,F"Your generosity, kindness, and
OL,13,Fsupport during this incredibly
OL,14,Fdifficult time means more to us than
OL,15,Fwords can express."
OL,17,FAn inquest heard that Chloe died from
OL,18,Fa stab wound to the chest.
OL,20,FThree people have been charged with
OL,21,Fher murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
