OL,3,CFuneral held for girl stabbed in street
OL,5,FKayla Smith, 18, of Kennerleigh
OL,6,FAvenue, 19-year-old Archie Rycroft, of
OL,7,FMiddleton Park Road, and a 17-year-old
OL,8,Fboy who cannot be named for legal
OL,9,Freasons, have all denied the charges.
